title: front_House
---
<<play_sound "OutsideHouseAmbience">>
<<play_sound "BusStopSteps">>
<<wait 1>>
<<if !has_flag("broken_house")>>
  The walk from the bus stop is so long...
  I need to get a car soon.
  Either way...
  It feels so good to be home. 
  ...
  Damn, it looks like I forgot to leave a light on...
<<else>>
  What the hell?
<<endif>>
===

title: front_DoorUnlock
---
<<if !has_flag("broken_house")>>
  <<play_sound "Deadbolt">>
  <<play_sound "frontDoor">>
  <<wait 1>>
  <<stop_sound "OutsideHouseAmbience">>
  <<load_scene_fade "livingRoom">>
<<else>>
  <<set_flag "inspect_broken_door">>
  Someone has broken down my door...
  I'm calling the police and staying with my mom...
  <<set_flag "game_over">>
  <<load_scene_fade "blackScreen">>
<<endif>>
===
